<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<ContentPage
	xmlns="http://xamarin.com/schemas/2014/forms"
	xmlns:x="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2009/xaml"
	xmlns:local="clr-namespace:PhillyBlotter"
	x:Class="PhillyBlotter.BetaWelcome"
	Title="Welcome" Padding="20,20,20,20">
	<ContentPage.Content>
		<ScrollView>
			<StackLayout>
				<Label
					HorizontalOptions="CenterAndExpand"
					FontSize="30"
					FontAttributes="Bold">PhillyBlotter</Label>
				<Label
					HorizontalOptions="CenterAndExpand"
					FontSize="Large">Welcome to Testing!</Label>
				<Label
					HorizontalOptions="Start"
					FontSize="Medium"
					FontAttributes="Bold"
					TextColor="#cc6600"
					HorizontalTextAlignment="Start">This test app will expire on December 30, 2016</Label>
				<Image
					HorizontalOptions="CenterAndExpand"
					Source="Images/filters.png">
				</Image>
				<Label
					HorizontalOptions="Start"
					FontSize="Medium"
					FontAttributes="Bold"
					HorizontalTextAlignment="Start">What are these circles?</Label>
				<Label
					HorizontalOptions="Start"
					FontSize="Small"
					HorizontalTextAlignment="Start">
H - Homicide     A - Assaults    R - Robbery
B - Burglary     T - Theft      R - Rape
Car - Auto crimes  
G - Gun/Weapon Violations  P-Prostition
O - Everything else (Narcotics / Vandalism / Parole violation, etc)
					
				</Label>
				<Label
					HorizontalOptions="Start"
					FontSize="Medium"
					FontAttributes="Bold"
					HorizontalTextAlignment="Start">What is PhillyBlotter?</Label>
				<Label
					HorizontalOptions="Start"
					HorizontalTextAlignment="Start">
PhillyBlotter is a crime app that allows you to see what crime has recently happened at your present location (within the last 10 days).  The data comes directly from the Philadelinquency Crime Center that aggregates data from the Philly police and Courtwatch.

PhillyBlotter will tell you if a suspect was charged with the reported crime and send you push notifications about important crimes and arrests that have happened near you as the data arrives to the Crime Center.
			</Label>
				<Label
					HorizontalOptions="Start"
					FontSize="Medium"
					FontAttributes="Bold"
					HorizontalTextAlignment="Start">What's in this edition</Label>
				<Label
					HorizontalOptions="Start"
					FontSize="Medium"
					HorizontalTextAlignment="Start">Presently the main app screen (the crime map) is done and so is the crime detail page.  As more functions are finished I will release new alpha builds to your phone.</Label>
				<Label
					HorizontalOptions="Start"
					FontSize="Medium"
					FontAttributes="Bold"
					HorizontalTextAlignment="Start">Features that are working for this release</Label>
				<Frame
					Padding="0,0,0,0">
					<StackLayout
						Orientation="Horizontal">
						<Image>
							<Image.Source>
						Images/yes.png
					</Image.Source>
						</Image>
						<Label>Main map screen</Label>
					</StackLayout>
				</Frame>
				<Frame
					Padding="0,0,0,0">
					<StackLayout
						Orientation="Horizontal">
						<Image>
							<Image.Source>
						Images/yes.png
					</Image.Source>
						</Image>
						<Label>Crime Detail</Label>
					</StackLayout>
				</Frame>
				<Frame
					Padding="0,0,0,0">
					<StackLayout
						Orientation="Horizontal">
						<Image>
							<Image.Source>
						Images/yes.png
					</Image.Source>
						</Image>
						<Label>Crime blotter in list view (map pins you can see converted to list)</Label>
					</StackLayout>
				</Frame>
				<Frame
					Padding="0,0,0,0">
					<StackLayout
						Orientation="Horizontal">
						<Image>
							<Image.Source>
						Images/yes.png
					</Image.Source>
						</Image>
						<Label>Settings screen</Label>
					</StackLayout>
				</Frame>				
				<Label
					HorizontalOptions="Start"
					FontSize="Medium"
					FontAttributes="Bold"
					HorizontalTextAlignment="Start">Still workin' on it! (For now these features are disabled on your phone)</Label>
				<Frame
					Padding="0,0,0,0">
					<StackLayout
						Orientation="Horizontal">
						<Image>
							<Image.Source>
						Images/no.png
					</Image.Source>
						</Image>
						<Label>Show arrests on map (change the circle pins to a shield)</Label>
					</StackLayout>
				</Frame>
				<Frame
					Padding="0,0,0,0">
					<StackLayout
						Orientation="Horizontal">
						<Image>
							<Image.Source>
						Images/no.png
					</Image.Source>
						</Image>
						<Label>Search (crime incidents and arrests based off dates, names, crime types)</Label>
					</StackLayout>
				</Frame>
				<Frame
					Padding="0,0,0,0">
					<StackLayout
						Orientation="Horizontal">
						<Image>
							<Image.Source>
						Images/no.png
					</Image.Source>
						</Image>
						<Label>Sharing a map pin(Facebook/Twitter/Email)</Label>
					</StackLayout>
				</Frame>
				<Frame
					Padding="0,0,0,0">
					<StackLayout
						Orientation="Horizontal">
						<Image>
							<Image.Source>
						Images/no.png
					</Image.Source>
						</Image>
						<Label>Push hot crime and hot arrest notifications</Label>
					</StackLayout>
				</Frame>
			</StackLayout>
		</ScrollView>
	</ContentPage.Content>
</ContentPage>